item.title: dang
item.description: (04:27:38) harper: i am work late ;) (04:28:00) Suresh: that's kinda obvious. (04:28:17) harper: hahaha i need to go home. i have been at work since 12. almost 17 hours. that is messed up. lakshmi has posted an interesting take on squidoo. I think the hype machine that is in full motion right now is pretty fun to watch. its amazing that seth is able to pull off what ad agencies woudl give a million dollars for.
